Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:50.36,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}倘若不变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:53.27,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}我将失去生存的意义
